- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory): The paper analyzes the complexity of a game, which is a topic in game theory.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the complexity of solving a game, which is related to artificial intelligence.
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry): The paper uses geometric shapes (bubbles) in the game, which is related to computational geometry.
